SpProgInd.description:
Special Programme Indicator

Indicates if the shipment has at least one item with preferential treatment or other reduced customs duty rates (e.g. FTA, Duty Exemption Regime). Preferential treatment means that an item get a reduced customs duty rate (compared to the standard customs duty rate for this product). {Yes, No}
Very often named as "preferential treatment" as well.

